                        <p class="mb-3">Since its beginning in 1964, Igloo has become synonymous for quality ice cream all across the country. With over 100 flavors, forms and shapes Igloo ice creams provide a rich, unmatched experience. Our slogan ‘a World of Great Taste’ reflects not only the delightful experience consumers have, but also the creative innovation, endless varieties, and our outstanding products </p>
                        <p class="mb-3"> Igloo never compromises on quality and taste, equipping our factories with the state-of-the-art technology – including installing extrusion, the only ice cream maker in Bangladesh to have done so – utilizing skilled human resources and using only the best ingredients. </p>
                        <p> Igloo ice cream is available nationwide in more than 20,000 retail outlets, supermarkets, and hypermarkets, and has a large number of corporate customers. Our ice cream range is growing day by day as we continue to lead the mindshare amongst consumers. In 2015, we have been ranked the no. 1 ice cream brand in Bangladesh by the Bangladesh Brand Forum</p>
